# As-Is Process Flowchart (Mermaid)

# Below is a flowchart you can view directly or copy into any Mermaid-compatible editor (like mermaid.live) to export as PNG/SVG.



flowchart TD
    A([Customer Submits Ticket]) --> B[CRM Creates Ticket]
    B --> C[Agent Opens Ticket Queue]
    C --> D[Agent Reads & Categorises Ticket]
    D --> E{Is Information Complete?}

    E -- No --> F[Request More Info]
    F --> G[Customer Provides Info]
    G --> E

    E -- Yes --> H{Can Agent Solve It?}

    H -- Yes --> I[Agent Resolves Ticket]
    I --> J[Agent Sends Final Reply]
    J --> K([Ticket Closed])
    K --> L([CSAT Survey Sent])

    H -- No --> M[Forward to Warehouse/Finance/Team Lead]
    M --> N[External Team Responds]
    N --> J
```

